text: Nice place, great massage, nothing to be complaint about. The masseuse Sue is very professional and friendly. Traditional full-body massage (with oil) is highly recommended. I personally loves the oil which the masseuse told me it is a traditional herbal massage oil (smells good). The place is clean and comfortable, located on the second floor, so you have to request an appointment so that the staff will guide you. Overall,  I'm very satisfied with Rhu Massage! Highly recommended!!

The best! Come with a friend and take a 90-minute traditional Malay massage. Feel very satisfied, the body feels light, the oil used is not sticky and comfortable. The place is very comfortable and clean, the staff is friendly. Thank you
The best traditional Malay massage so far is the same as in the villages and the massage therapist is also experienced.. very satisfied
